title: 26 - Liz Miele
itunes:title: 26 - Liz Miele
description: Liz Miele! You may know her from her viral YouTube clips, Comedy Central’s “Live at Gotham” and “This Week at the Comedy Cellar,” NPR’s “Wait Wait Don’t Tell Me,” and much more. We’re talking about how cats are the best and the worst, what it’s like to have vets as parents, our favorite animated movies, and much much more. Here are five words to describe this episode: do not smoke loose weed.
